title: Wednesday Pt1: Rams repeat? MVP Predictions, Biggest mystery, and Don't Worry Darling
itunes:title: Wednesday Pt1: Rams repeat? MVP Predictions, Biggest mystery, and Don't Worry Darling
description:
Part One of the Good Morning Football Podcast begins with the Rams chances of returning to the Super Bowl.  Hosts Jamie Erdahl, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Super Bowl Champion Jason McCourty continue Prediction Week with each selecting a different candidate for MVP.  Kyle explains why the Patriots could be the biggest mystery for this upcoming season. The table debates who will silence the critics in Week 1, while Peter wants to tell Dolphins fans 'Dont Worry Darling'.  Stay tuned for Part Two!

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
